## Fun Fact About Me
I can sleep for 15 hours in one go! 

</code></pre>

			<h5>üéØ Workshop Goals</h5>
			<ul>
				<li>Practice forking repositories</li>
				<li>Learn proper commit message conventions</li>
				<li>Create meaningful pull requests</li>
				<li>Experience code review processes</li>
				<li>Understand deployment workflows</li>
			</ul>

			<p>
				Ready to get started? <a href="/blog">Check out the blog</a> to see existing posts 
				and what yours will look like once merged!
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
